### Description
The dataset contains information of 452 patients in a study group. 

### Attributes
* STUDYID = ID of the study group 
* USUBJID = ID of the subject/patient 
* AGE = Age of the subject 
* SEX = Gender of the subject 
* RACE = Race of the subject 
* ACTARM = Actual treatment arm variable for the subject (kind of treatment the subject recieved) 
* ACTARMCD = Actual treatment arm variable code
